OL,3,CMiddle school saved from closure with
OL,4,Cyear groups set to expand
OL,6,FA North East middle school has been
OL,7,Fsaved from closure and will expand its
OL,8,Fyear groups in order to secure its
OL,9,Ffuture.
OL,11,FNorth Tyneside Council bosses signed
OL,12,Foff on plans to expand Monkseaton
OL,13,FMiddle School's year groups from 5-8
OL,14,Fto 5-11 on Monday (16 March).
OL,16,FThe school will introduce Year 9 in
OL,17,F2027, then Years 10 and 11, the Local
OL,18,FDemocracy Reporting Service reports.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
