PN,42602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773857158
OL,3,CMiddle school saved from closure with
OL,4,Cyear groups set to expand
OL,6,FIt is hoped the phased plan will allow
OL,7,Ffor gradual growth, a balanced Key
OL,8,FStage 4 curriculum, as well as
OL,9,Fenabling pupils to stay on at the
OL,10,Fschool until 16.
OL,12,FMonkseaton Middle School was one of
OL,13,Fseveral schools in North Tyneside
OL,14,Ffaced with the prospect of closure in
OL,15,Fthe council's original plans in
OL,16,FOctober 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773857158
OL,3,CMiddle school saved from closure with
OL,4,Cyear groups set to expand
OL,6,FThe local authority cited low birth
OL,7,Frates, surplus places, and the
OL,8,Fsubsequent impacts on school budgets
OL,9,Fas major contributing factors to the
OL,10,Fplans which spread throughout North
OL,11,FTyneside.
OL,13,FThe move sparked public outcry, with a
OL,14,Fpetition to save Monkseaton Middle
OL,15,FSchool gaining more than 1,200
OL,16,Fsignatures and over #5,700 raised to
OL,17,Fhelp finance a campaign to retain the
OL,18,Fschool, including the prospect of
OL,19,Ffunding a legal challenge. The
OL,20,FGoFundMe states any surplus money
OL,21,Fwould be handed directly to the school.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42604
