CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773857158
OL,3,CMiddle school saved from closure with
OL,4,Cyear groups set to expand
OL,6,FBy November last year, the school was
OL,7,Foffered the opportunity to find
OL,8,Falternative solutions and later
OL,9,Fpresent them to the local authority
OL,10,Ffor consideration.
OL,12,FA council report into the new
OL,13,Fproposals published last week stated
OL,14,Fwhile the plans did not completely
OL,15,Fresolve the wider pupil number
OL,16,Fpressures, it would provide a
OL,17,F"meaningful contribution" to the issue.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773857158
OL,3,CMiddle school saved from closure with
OL,4,Cyear groups set to expand
OL,6,FThe proposals were recommended for
OL,7,Fapproval. It is also estimated the
OL,8,Fmove would also turn around the
OL,9,Fschool's projected deficit of #118,000
OL,10,Fin year one, to a surplus of over
OL,11,F#230,000 by year three.
OL,13,FHeadteacher Kirsty Nichols-Mackay
OL,14,Fsaid: "As a school community, we are
OL,15,Fabsolutely delighted by this decision.
OL,16,FI want to express my sincere thanks to
OL,17,Four families, whose engagement and
OL,18,Fsupport throughout this process have
OL,19,Fbeen invaluable, and to our Governing
OL,20,FBody for their unwavering dedication.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773857158
OL,3,CMiddle school saved from closure with
OL,4,Cyear groups set to expand
OL,6,F"I am equally grateful to our
OL,7,Fexceptional staff, whose commitment to
OL,8,Four pupils underpins everything we do.
OL,10,F"Extending our age range allows us to
OL,11,Fcontinue meeting the needs of all our
OL,12,Fyoung people while strengthening the
OL,13,Funique offer that makes Monkseaton
OL,14,FMiddle so special: a smaller, more
OL,15,Fpersonal setting, offering high
OL,16,Fquality teaching and learning for all
OL,17,Fchildren. This change gives families
OL,18,Freal choice and enables pupils to
OL,19,Fremain in an inclusive environment
OL,20,Fright through to age 16."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
