PN,42607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1773857158
OL,3,CMiddle school saved from closure with
OL,4,Cyear groups set to expand
OL,6,FCouncillor Steven Phillips, cabinet
OL,7,Fmember for education, inclusion,
OL,8,Femployment and skills, said: "We're
OL,9,Fpleased that a positive and
OL,10,Fsustainable solution has been found
OL,11,Ffor Monkseaton Middle School.
OL,13,F"The governorled proposal keeps the
OL,14,Fschool open, supports parental choice
OL,15,Fand gives pupils the option to stay in
OL,16,Fa smaller, inclusive setting through
OL,17,Fto GCSEs. We'd like to thank everyone
OL,18,Fwho took part in the consultation and
OL,19,Fhelped shape this outcome."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
