OL,3,CMiddle school saved from closure with
OL,4,Cyear groups set to expand
OL,6,FThe school will now begin preparing
OL,7,Ffor the phased introduction of Year 9
OL,8,Fand Key Stage 4, with the new age
OL,9,Frange taking effect from September
OL,10,F2027.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/8
